---
title: "Love"
date: "03-31-2020"
categories: [poems]
title-block-banner: false
---

<div class = "poem">
* Love is a distance
* that wants to be closed
* like a door by those
* who forget it breathes
* in the space between
* what was forgotten
* and the suddenly
* remembered.
* &nbsp;
* I forgot. And then
* I remembered.
</div>